## Project Identity
name: "Flutter App"
description: "Flutter/Dart application"
version: "1.0.0"

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Flutter
- Language: Dart
- State Management: Riverpod
- Testing: flutter_test

## Coding Style
- Use const constructors where possible
- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Use named parameters for clarity
- Follow Dart lint rules

## Constraints
- No hardcoded strings — use l10n
- Handle all async errors
- Write widget tests for all screens
